+    operations on non-scaled integers. Floating point divide should use
+    `spirv.Tosa.Reciprocal` and `spirv.Tosa.Mul`. Quantized integer divide
+    should use `spirv.Tosa.Table`(for $ 1/x $) and `spirv.Tosa.Mul`.
